# BobaClaw Rust

- Match existing crate boundaries; prefer extending over new abstractions.
- Gateway process must not run untrusted tools directly — use executor profiles (ADR 003).
- After `.rs` edits: hooks run `cargo fmt --all` automatically; before handoff run `make fmt-check` (CI runs `cargo fmt --all -- --check`).
- Run `cargo clippy --workspace --all-targets -- -D warnings` and `cargo test` for touched crates.
- Minimal diffs; no drive-by refactors in unrelated modules.
